race.comment: VERRUCKT (4) has a fair record and proved too classy last time to win by 1.75 lengths at this track in a handy 22.05 beating BIG KELCE. Can continue on his winning ways. SHINE ON SKI (8) jumped well and was in the mix early before fading out of it late when 7th over 380m at this track in Grade 5 company. Expected to run well. TOMMY FROM MARS (2) was responsible for a modest effort most recently when fifth at this track over 380m behind She's Spirited (22.45) in a Grade 5. Scored at his previous run. Leading chance. TILLY'S SON (7) was in the money last start and wasn't beaten far - should feature again.

runners.name: Big Kelce
